.SH NAME
devm_pci_remap_cfgspace \- Managed pci_remap_cfgspace()
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void __iomem *" devm_pci_remap_cfgspace
.BI "(struct device *dev "  ","
.BI "resource_size_t offset "  ","
.BI "resource_size_t size "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "dev" 12
Generic device to remap IO address for
.IP "offset" 12
Resource address to map
.IP "size" 12
Size of map
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Managed \fBpci_remap_cfgspace\fP.  Map is automatically unmapped on driver
detach.
